  "remarks": "JSC “Scientific and Production Association ‘Pribor’ named after S.S. Golembiovsky” is a State corporate belonging to the “Technodinamika” which is part of the “Rostec” complex. It manufactures cartridges and rounds for weapons which are used in the Russian war of aggression against Ukraine. Therefore, JSC “Scientific and Production Association “Pribor” named after S.S. Golembiovsky” is supporting materially actions which undermine and threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
